snippet.title: 7 Things You Need To Do In Fort Joy - Divinity Original Sin 2
snippet.description:
Divinity: Original Sin II is a game you could potentially spend hours and hours in a single area, and still miss a ton of cool stuff. So we've come up with 7 things you might've missed from the game's starting zone, Fort Joy.


Check out our GameSpot review of Divinity: Original Sin II: 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wI-NBfk3mM4

Watch 7 Essential Tips for Divinity: Original Sin 2:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p4xobSGCjoM

Or just go to our Divinity Original Sin 2 playlist!
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YJyXQxgNVhU&list=PLpg6WLs8kxGPWmwweYIRmVYQqcKLFn5Is

https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.cbsinteractive.gamespot.tt
